CHAPTER 4 \'96 SYSTEM DESIGN\
4.1 Basic Modules\
Bug Overflow is composed of the following major functional modules:\
Authentication Module\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qj\partightenfactor0
\cf0 Handles user registration, login, logout, and token management. Uses JWT with HTTP-only cookies for secure session management. Includes password reset via email OTP.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 Question Module\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qj\partightenfactor0
\cf0 Manages the full lifecycle of questions: creation, editing, deletion, tagging, and voting. Supports rich-text formatting via React Quill and full-text search by keyword or tag.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 Answer Module\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qj\partightenfactor0
\cf0 Allows users to submit formatted answers, vote on them, and have them accepted by the question owner. The accepted answer is highlighted and the answerer gains +15 reputation.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 Comment Module\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qj\partightenfactor0
\cf0 Provides threaded comment discussions on both questions and answers. Comments support plain text and are paginated for performance.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 Article Module\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qj\partightenfactor0
\cf0 Enables users to publish longer technical articles with rich-text formatting. Articles can be upvoted and commented upon.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 Notification Module\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qj\partightenfactor0
\cf0 Automatically generates notifications for user interactions including votes, new answers, accepted answers, and comments. Tracks read/unread status.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 Reputation & Badge Module\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qj\partightenfactor0
\cf0 Automatically calculates and updates user reputation on vote/accept events. Awards badges at milestones: Informed (1), Enthusiast (10), Veteran (50), Expert (200).\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 Bookmark Module\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qj\partightenfactor0
\cf0 Allows users to save questions to a personal bookmark list for future reference.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 User Profile Module\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qj\partightenfactor0
\cf0 Displays user statistics, questions, answers, articles, and earned badges. Allows profile editing including avatar upload and bio.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
\cf0 Search Module\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\qj\partightenfactor0
\cf0 Provides full-text search across questions using MongoDB text indexes. Supports tag-based filtering and displays results with relevance ranking.\
\pard\pardeftab720\pardirnatural\partightenfactor0
